{"tid":92631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"資深空姐 教大家追空姐 8 招","createTime":"2017-01-23T17:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T05:00:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9988d2ee0fbd0b7f93a5a4707db6f5a404518fa","tid":92631,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:17:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 資深空姐 教大家追空姐 8 招</span> <br />\n<br />\n姐有如揮著翅膀的女孩。在機上與心儀空姐華麗邂逅，即時心花怒放，但又不知怎樣與她打開天窗? <br />\n<br />\n縱橫空港15年的已婚空姐兼作家Heather Poole向大家告解，原來追求空姐並非想得太遠．她與丈夫也是始於高空三萬尺的一面之緣。空姐雖然很忙，但只要加大力度，簡單的 8 招就可讓她對你另眼相看，各位男士不容錯失!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/w600/20140221180920_0_814554-d762aad6-7729-11e3-ae56-4ce697eaa265.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Fw600%2F20140221180920_0_814554-d762aad6-7729-11e3-ae56-4ce697eaa265.jpg&h=a6a8c253&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"780797fa289fa1efb560dbe13df25ae47b5fe7bc","tid":92631,"uid":78118,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:17:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c56739873268f0f58d477a2d61f99738a8ce1d5","tid":92631,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"1. 眼神交流<br />\n空姐每日要說幾百次「你好」、「歡迎」，會回應她的人卻寥寥可数。禮貌微笑回應吧，再加點親切的眼神交流，能在空姐心目中留下良好印象。另外，多說「麻煩你」、「謝謝」等客氣語，亦會加分!<br />\n<br />\n2. 別炫耀「飛行常客狀態」(frequent flier status)<br />\n航空公司有一套區分客人的飛行里數及等級的系統，好些人喜歡炫耀這身份，其實空姐一早已知，過份炫耀只會令她叫你「借過」。<br />\n<br />\n3. 幫助其他乘客<br />\n男士們見到乘客將行李抬入行李櫃有因難時，不妨在這刻不容媛之際幫忙一下。空姐們見到會標籤你為好人，是成為Honey的好對象。<br />\n<br />\n4. 請扣好安全帶<br />\n空姐們要不斷叫乘客扣好安全帶，甚至要多番唇舌解釋、爭論是很累人的，想讓空姐喜喜，扣好安全帶吧。<br />\n<br />\n5. 不要讓空姐等你<br />\n當空姐拖著餐車隆重登場為你介紹飛機餐時，請立即除下耳機；在她們準備放下飲品和食物之前，就應該清理好餐桌的物品，不要讓空姐停下來等你太久喔。<br />\n<br />\n6. 善於分享<br />\n空姐的工時很長，航空公司於短途機上又不會向空中服務員提供膳食，如果有男乘客為又餓又累的空姐分享，哪怕是一粒朱古力也萬歲，肯定甜在心頭。<br />\n<br />\n7. 不要狂按Call Bell<br />\n空中服務員每15分鐘就會巡視機艙一次，如非緊急事，就不要好事多為狂按呼叫鈴(Call Bell)，空姐話Call Bell和999的原理一樣，建議請勿濫用。<br />\n<br />\n8. 大膽踏出第一步<br />\n有說「空姐經常被搭訕」? 只是典型的想法，但現實非然，至少她們希望會搭訕的男士並不會這樣做。如果你真的對某位空姐特别感興趣，不要怯，即使不能譜出3萬尺高空情綠，與空姐交個密友也不錯呢!"},{"pid":"d66c2a51bbb81df82a61066ddbc3de68b8cdd30e","tid":92631,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"追空姐做Sp<br />\n玩完就閃啦<br />\n<br />\n飛雞, 都大把人上過的"},{"pid":"db017de8353144f8ffd648f0fcab772b53ef6d42","tid":92631,"uid":57490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:23:42.000Z","msg":"錢錢錢錢錢錢錢錢"},{"pid":"2558ba52396b925c2ace38bdfa82b5968152ce5f","tid":92631,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:33:12.000Z","msg":"0. 坐頭等位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699b6a944de6c8e39ac48eb220581a944eb8aeac","tid":92631,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:36:46.000Z","msg":"呢8招似係教大家咪撚阻住空姐做嘢多啲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d435c5d5f82cf6729de1975ec183cd4103fea53","tid":92631,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:42:15.000Z","msg":"追空姐定做空姐隻兵"},{"pid":"545c00c1263b1d2552b1d31a6db751d537929833","tid":92631,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:43:34.000Z","msg":"空姐雖然很忙，但只要加大力度<br />\n<br />\n見到呢句笑撚咗出嚟，咩中文嚟"},{"pid":"4dca15c5b9c6cd263f6eb5d1e02c2c407b090157","tid":92631,"uid":77605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:43:47.000Z","msg":"做機師咪得"},{"pid":"ee742ce714bec19ba3fe00804302a2f911ae440f","tid":92631,"uid":51340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:49:19.000Z","msg":"又咪侍應一個，睇到自己咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fbeb07523121175e4288fbf3b6205192a15834b","tid":92631,"uid":20328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:29:12.000Z","msg":"Your face your fate <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05958fdcb4039ab274703475c67d312c1b8c5c0b","tid":92631,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:46:15.000Z","msg":"生炒骨"},{"pid":"a8e4ecde33029fe264cc2c440f6a2b46acf3230f","tid":92631,"uid":67656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:00:12.000Z","msg":"Old news is so 唔識串"},{"pid":"36718ae8cb3b1aa5521f3952b5acd6a8baf6fab5","tid":92631,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢8招似係教大家咪撚阻住空姐做嘢多啲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真"},{"pid":"2058964577a4e91b9740bf98fc7fa51f77d94eb0","tid":92631,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:05:52.000Z","msg":"乜有人稀罕追空姐架咩<br />\n點解特登要去教人追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e4257f02e28841872e5d34a922d99b70dfa45c","tid":92631,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本冇人想追"},{"pid":"2b0956ffc4f76e655b3b1bfe36327109d3b6d12d","tid":92631,"uid":34256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等啲飛雞做小啲野"},{"pid":"d091d0ee582dc9d0237ce0568a6e739ec975ca28","tid":92631,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:11:05.000Z","msg":"On9，當自己係上菜？"},{"pid":"b27ee056f47276d07057d5c39499685747038c4c","tid"