f3b37a7dc5b4d7","tid":92631,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑死...差唔多樣樣野都係叫你幫佢減輕工作負擔<br />\n不如索性調轉，空姐坐係度客人服侍佢好過啦<br />\n唔想做咪出聲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾錢算啦"},{"pid":"29d5b0fb79971f8ab71f30523f397327b056940a","tid":92631,"uid":39295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 資深空姐 教大家追空姐 8 招</span> <br />\n<br />\n姐有如<span style=\"color: red;\">揮著翅膀的女孩</span>。在機上與心儀空姐<span style=\"color: red;\">華麗邂逅</span>，即時<span style=\"color: red;\">心花怒放</span>，但又不知怎樣與她打開<span style=\"color: red;\">天窗</span>? <br />\n<br />\n縱橫空港15年的已婚空姐兼作家Heather Poole向大家<span style=\"color: red;\">告解</span>，原來追求空姐並非<span style=\"color: red;\">想得太遠</span>．她與丈夫也是始於高空三萬尺的<span style=\"color: red;\">一面之緣</span>。空姐雖然很忙，但只要<span style=\"color: red;\">加大力度</span>，簡單的 8 招就可讓她對你<span style=\"color: red;\">另眼相看</span>，各位男士<span style=\"color: red;\">不容錯失</span>!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/w600/20140221180920_0_814554-d762aad6-7729-11e3-ae56-4ce697eaa265.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Fw600%2F20140221180920_0_814554-d762aad6-7729-11e3-ae56-4ce697eaa265.jpg&h=a6a8c253&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bfad61516e569d9a04d220d90fd124ce8148b13a","tid":92631,"uid":39295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 資深空姐 教大家追空姐 8 招</span> <br />\n<br />\n姐有如<span style=\"color: red;\">揮著翅膀的女孩</span>。在機上與心儀空姐<span style=\"color: red;\">華麗邂逅</span>，即時<span style=\"color: red;\">心花怒放</span>，但又不知怎樣與她打開<span style=\"color: red;\">天窗</span>? <br />\n<br />\n縱橫<span style=\"color: red;\">空港</span>15年的已婚空姐兼作家Heather Poole向大家<span style=\"color: red;\">告解</span>，原來追求空姐並非<span style=\"color: red;\">想得太遠</span>．她與丈夫也是始於高空三萬尺的<span style=\"color: red;\">一面之緣</span>。空姐雖然很忙，但只要<span style=\"color: red;\">加大力度</span>，簡單的 8 招就可讓她對你<span style=\"color: red;\">另眼相看</span>，各位男士<span style=\"color: red;\">不容錯失</span>!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/w600/20140221180920_0_814554-d762aad6-7729-11e3-ae56-4ce697eaa265.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Fw600%2F20140221180920_0_814554-d762aad6-7729-11e3-ae56-4ce697eaa265.jpg&h=a6a8c253&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e1ee42de1c9897c6d628f962b63ef63bc90bfd90","tid":92631,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:16:11.000Z","msg":"戇鳩"},{"pid":"0c222fe72007556a4cefca7a94015132204499b3","tid":92631,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:17:30.000Z","msg":"直接同人講最好唔洗做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03df54e9b34ef2c964ee8148cc4d21eaf430ed34","tid":92631,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:19:43.000Z","msg":"錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3357ee3149ce6994ca266376e44ddcb225fa2d","tid":92631,"uid":17215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"篇野一定係D空姐自己打架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfe1fda0e677dd89bd42ee531ee086cdeb35552","tid":92631,"uid":39295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 眼神交流<br />\n空姐每日要說幾百次「你好」、「歡迎」，會回應她的人卻寥寥可数。禮貌微笑回應吧，再加點親切的眼神交流，能在空姐心目中留下良好印象。另外，多說「<span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩你</span>」、「謝謝」等客氣語，亦會加分!<br />\n<br />\n2. 別炫耀「飛行常客狀態」(frequent flier status)<br />\n航空公司有一套區分客人的飛行里數及等級的系統，好些人喜歡炫耀這身份，其實空姐一早已知，過份炫耀只會令她叫你「<span style=\"color: red;\">借過</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n3. 幫助其他乘客<br />\n男士們見到乘客將行李抬入行李櫃有因難時，不妨在這<span style=\"color: red;\">刻不容媛</span>之際幫忙一下。空姐們見到會標籤你為好人，是成為Honey的好對象。<br />\n<br />\n4. 請扣好安全帶<br />\n空姐們要不斷叫乘客扣好安全帶，甚至要多番唇舌解釋、爭論是很累人的，想讓空姐<span style=\"color: red;\">喜喜</span>，扣好安全帶吧。<br />\n<br />\n5. 不要讓空姐等你<br />\n當空姐拖著餐車<span style=\"color: red;\">隆重登場</span>為你介紹飛機餐時，請立即除下耳機；在她們準備放下飲品和食物之前，就應該清理好餐桌的物品，不要讓空姐停下來等你太久喔。<br />\n<br />\n6. 善於分享<br />\n空姐的工時很長，航空公司於短途機上又不會向空中服務員提供膳食，如果有男乘客為又餓又累的空姐分享，哪怕是一粒<span style=\"color: red;\">朱古力</span>也<span style=\"color: red;\">萬歲</span>，肯定甜在心頭。<br />\n<br />\n7. 不要狂按Call Bell<br />\n空中服務員每15分鐘就會巡視機艙一次，如非緊急事，就不要<span style=\"color: red;\">好事多為</span>狂按呼叫鈴(Call Bell)，空姐話Call Bell和999的原理一樣，建議請勿濫用。<br />\n<br />\n8. 大膽踏出第一步<br />\n有說「空姐經常被搭訕」? 只是典型的想法，但現實非然，至少她們希望會搭訕的男士並不會這樣做。如果你真的對某位空姐特别感興趣，不要<span style=\"color: red;\">怯</span>，即使不能譜出3萬尺高空情綠，與空姐交個<span style=\"color: red;\">密友</span>也不錯呢!</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c6e817525aab04f6558ba5f990ea2e82ec14c69b","tid":92631,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:26:16.000Z","msg":"表面教人點追飛雞，暗則屌D客平時有幾煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076f45d4b19e348289512fd7c8f9b0b245850187","tid":92631,"uid":66187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"飛雞都要教點追？一句都尾咪係錢，坐first class"},{"pid":"03885bee8a1d112eb9193f65f01e912fe6d063fb","tid":92631,"uid":44948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"㩒call bell 分享條撚你奶下濕下口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b772c41358336b9c98cebd377dd17dd3daa2b5bc","tid":92631,"uid":32686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T02:36:46.000Z","msg":"有個空姐係咁迫我拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj